<plot>The Taylor family is so caught up in planning for the holiday that they forget the true meaning of Christmas. Baking cookies, shopping, decorating, parties all take center stage in the families hurried "daze" before Christmas. The frantic situation comes to a head when bubbles, a broken wiseman, the family dog, and the local fire department turn their annual Christmas party into a three ring circus.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?552229</url></doc>
